The /live/portfolio/read API provides a response in the following format:

200 Success

LivePortfolioResponse Model - Contains holdings and cash of the live algorithm in the request criteria.
portfolio Portfolio object
Portfolio object with the holdings and cash information.
success boolean
Indicate if the API request was successful.
errors string Array
List of errors with the API call.
Example 
{
  "portfolio": {
    "holdings": {
      "a": 0,
      "q": 0,
      "p": 0,
      "v": 0,
      "u": 0,
      "up": 0
    },
    "cash": {
      "securitySymbols": [
        "object"
      ],
      "symbol": "string",
      "amount": 0,
      "conversionRate": 0,
      "currencySymbol": "string",
      "valueInAccountCurrency": 0
    }
  },
  "success": true,
  "errors": [
    "string"
  ]
}
Portfolio Model - Portfolio object with the holdings and cash information.
holdings Holding object
Dictionary of algorithm holdings information, where the key is the Symbol Id.
cash Cash object
Dictionary of algorithm cash currencies information, where the key is the currency ticker.
Example 
{
  "holdings": {
    "a": 0,
    "q": 0,
    "p": 0,
    "v": 0,
    "u": 0,
    "up": 0
  },
  "cash": {
    "securitySymbols": [
      "object"
    ],
    "symbol": "string",
    "amount": 0,
    "conversionRate": 0,
    "currencySymbol": "string",
    "valueInAccountCurrency": 0
  }
}
Holding Model - Summary of asset holding.
a number
Average purchase price of the holding in the currency it trades in.
q number
Quantity of the asset.
p number
Current market price of the asset in the currency it trades in.
v number
Current market value of the holding.
u number
Unrealized profit/loss of the position.
up number
Unrealized profit/loss percentage of the position.
Example 
{
  "a": 0,
  "q": 0,
  "p": 0,
  "v": 0,
  "u": 0,
  "up": 0
}
Cash Model - Represents a holding of a currency in cash.
securitySymbols object Array
/.
symbol string
Gets the symbol used to represent this cash.
amount number
Gets or sets the amount of cash held.
conversionRate number
The currency conversion rate to the account base currency.
currencySymbol string
The symbol of the currency.
valueInAccountCurrency number
The value of the currency cash in the account base currency.
Example 
{
  "securitySymbols": [
    "object"
  ],
  "symbol": "string",
  "amount": 0,
  "conversionRate": 0,
  "currencySymbol": "string",
  "valueInAccountCurrency": 0
}

401 Authentication Error

UnauthorizedError Model - Unauthorized response from the API. Key is missing, invalid, or timestamp is too old for hash.
www_authenticate string
Header
